instructions: ping - The latency for the bot. The API latency is the bot and the server.
play <newActivity> - Sets a new activity to play. [Admin only]
say <text> - Makes the bot send a message.
kick <member> <reason> - Allows administrators to kick memebers. [Admin only]
ban <member> <reason> - Allows administrators to ban memebers. [Admin only]
purge <number> - Allows for bulk deletion of messages from all users up to 100. [Admin only]
prefix <newPrefix> - Sets the prefix to whatever the user wants. [Admin only]
filter <on/off> or <add/remove> <word> - Sets the automatic swear filter on/off or adds/removes a word from the swear filter. [Admin only]
